1
00:01:10,360 --> 00:01:12,760
Shanshui Group, get out of Dayang Village!

2
00:01:12,960 --> 00:01:15,360
Shanshui Group, get out of Dayang Village!

3
00:01:59,320 --> 00:02:00,120
Who are you?

4
00:02:00,960 --> 00:02:01,920
What do you want?

5
00:02:02,280 --> 00:02:03,120
Where is this?

6
00:02:03,280 --> 00:02:04,340
What are you doing?

7
00:02:17,240 --> 00:02:18,440
I'm sorry, brothers.

8
00:02:18,480 --> 00:02:20,360
I can't see. Where are my glasses?

9
00:02:29,960 --> 00:02:31,920
Laid-off miners.

10
00:02:35,920 --> 00:02:39,040
You three are laid-off workers, right?

11
00:02:39,200 --> 00:02:40,240
Let me explain.

12
00:02:41,600 --> 00:02:43,079
The higher-ups ordered the shutdown.

13
00:02:43,079 --> 00:02:44,610
And restructuring, right?

14
00:02:44,880 --> 00:02:46,120
It wasn't my idea.

15
00:02:46,120 --> 00:02:47,579
Kidnapping me won't help.

16
00:02:48,120 --> 00:02:49,050
Stop hitting me!

17
00:02:49,480 --> 00:02:50,280
Don't hit me!

18
00:02:55,160 --> 00:02:56,440
The severance pay.

19
00:02:58,680 --> 00:02:59,920
The severance pay...

20
00:03:00,000 --> 00:03:02,130
Shanshui Group is supposed to pay you.

21
00:03:02,240 --> 00:03:03,640
You can't ask me for it.

22
00:03:03,640 --> 00:03:04,200
I don't have any money either.

23
00:03:04,200 --> 00:03:05,320
What do you want?

24
00:03:05,480 --> 00:03:06,400
What?

25
00:03:06,680 --> 00:03:09,200
It hurts! I'll pay! I'll pay!

26
00:03:10,480 --> 00:03:11,640
I'll pay!

27
00:03:12,880 --> 00:03:13,920
I'll pay!

28
00:03:19,520 --> 00:03:21,200
The laid-off workers'...

29
00:03:22,960 --> 00:03:23,880
No, no.

30
00:03:24,400 --> 00:03:25,200
Brother.

31
00:03:25,800 --> 00:03:27,040
I can't afford that.

32
00:03:27,360 --> 00:03:29,079
The severance pay for all the workers...

33
00:03:29,079 --> 00:03:30,280
It would be 2 million.

34
00:03:30,560 --> 00:03:32,120
Where am I supposed to find 2 million?

35
00:03:32,120 --> 00:03:32,840
Right?

36
00:03:32,840 --> 00:03:33,680
You can't...

37
00:03:40,840 --> 00:03:41,640
What are you doing?

38
00:03:41,640 --> 00:03:43,280
This is illegal.

39
00:03:44,440 --> 00:03:45,280
What are you doing?

40
00:03:45,280 --> 00:03:46,200
What are you doing?

41
00:03:46,200 --> 00:03:47,130
What do you want?

42
00:03:47,840 --> 00:03:48,600
What are you doing?

43
00:03:48,600 --> 00:03:49,240
Don't!

44
00:04:09,120 --> 00:04:10,760
I'll pay!

45
00:04:12,920 --> 00:04:15,120
I'll give you whatever I have! I'll pay!

46
00:04:15,360 --> 00:04:16,620
Can I make a phone call?

47
00:04:29,080 --> 00:04:31,040
You don't know how to use it, right, brother?

48
00:04:31,040 --> 00:04:31,840
Listen to me.

49
00:04:33,159 --> 00:04:34,890
First, the one on the far right.

50
00:04:36,159 --> 00:04:36,960
Yes.

51
00:04:37,720 --> 00:04:39,120
Scroll down. Down.

52
00:04:39,240 --> 00:04:40,520
Xie Lao'er. Yes, yes.

53
00:04:43,840 --> 00:04:44,640
Lao'er.

54
00:04:45,720 --> 00:04:47,360
Get up and go to the study.

55
00:04:47,760 --> 00:04:49,280
Take out all the money.

56
00:04:49,280 --> 00:04:50,000
Yes.

57
00:04:50,240 --> 00:04:51,240
Take it to the Miners' Union.

58
00:04:51,240 --> 00:04:53,640
Distribute it to all the laid-off workers.

59
00:04:54,080 --> 00:04:56,540
I haven't finished speaking, brother. I...

60
00:05:01,440 --> 00:05:02,570
Can you let me go now?

61
00:05:02,880 --> 00:05:04,560
No, no, no! The alarm! The alarm!

62
00:05:04,560 --> 00:05:06,420
Don't be scared. Don't be scared.

63
00:05:06,880 --> 00:05:08,210
I can't take it anymore.

64
00:05:33,200 --> 00:05:34,200
Yang Gang, you...

65
00:05:38,520 --> 00:05:40,680
Xiao Li, make sure you record this.

66
00:05:40,680 --> 00:05:41,600
I'll take notes.

67
00:05:41,600 --> 00:05:43,600
What were you guys doing last night?

68
00:05:46,000 --> 00:05:46,880
At 11:00.

69
00:05:47,680 --> 00:05:48,480
Are you sure?

70
00:05:48,960 --> 00:05:49,960
Very sure.

71
00:05:50,800 --> 00:05:53,320
The watch I wore last night has an alarm.

72
00:05:54,000 --> 00:05:55,200
Every night at 11:00.

73
00:05:56,040 --> 00:05:57,500
I have to take my medicine.

74
00:05:58,040 --> 00:05:59,170
Last night at 11:00.

75
00:05:59,320 --> 00:06:00,600
Where were the three of you?

76
00:06:00,600 --> 00:06:01,460
What did you do?

77
00:06:01,960 --> 00:06:03,280
I... The three of us...

78
00:06:07,200 --> 00:06:08,000
Come on.

79
00:06:08,400 --> 00:06:09,360
Yongzi just finished his.

80
00:06:09,360 --> 00:06:10,920
You have to take a big gulp. It's mandatory.

81
00:06:10,920 --> 00:06:11,240
Okay, okay.

82
00:06:11,240 --> 00:06:11,960
Yang Gang!

83
00:06:13,600 --> 00:06:15,040
It's 11 o'clock. Why aren't you asleep?

84
00:06:15,040 --> 00:06:16,160
What's all the noise?

85
00:06:16,160 --> 00:06:17,040
Come up and have a drink.

86
00:06:17,040 --> 00:06:18,000
Come on, Mrs. Chen.

87
00:06:18,000 --> 00:06:19,800
Bunch of drunks. Lunatics.

88
00:06:22,240 --> 00:06:24,280
Four deuces. Who can beat that?

89
00:06:34,600 --> 00:06:36,240
We've recorded the details.

90
00:06:36,320 --> 00:06:37,360
Don't disturb the neighbors again.

91
00:06:37,360 --> 00:06:38,720
We won't.

92
00:06:39,040 --> 00:06:42,120
The three of us really had too much fun drinking last night.

93
00:06:42,120 --> 00:06:43,960
And we disturbed Mrs. Chen's sleep.

94
00:06:43,960 --> 00:06:45,240
But we promise,

95
00:06:45,240 --> 00:06:47,360
it won't happen again.

96
00:06:47,360 --> 00:06:48,080
Secondly,

97
00:06:48,080 --> 00:06:49,280
Mr. Xiao just said

98
00:06:49,800 --> 00:06:52,200
that we kidnapped him at 11 o'clock.

99
00:06:52,640 --> 00:06:53,920
But at 11 o'clock last night,

100
00:06:53,920 --> 00:06:56,159
we were with Officer Li.

101
00:06:56,159 --> 00:06:57,560
He can vouch for us.

102
00:06:57,760 --> 00:06:59,240
That's right.

103
00:07:00,160 --> 00:07:02,800
I did see Yang Gang at 11 last night.

104
00:07:02,920 --> 00:07:04,780
Yang Gaoyong and Luo Zhengqiang.

105
00:07:04,960 --> 00:07:06,560
You're in on it with them, aren't you?

106
00:07:06,560 --> 00:07:07,960
You're a police officer.

107
00:07:09,120 --> 00:07:09,920
Yes.

108
00:07:10,720 --> 00:07:12,600
It's all down in black and white.

109
00:07:13,360 --> 00:07:14,160
So, Mr. Xiao,

110
00:07:14,160 --> 00:07:16,120
you must have been mistaken.

111
00:07:17,680 --> 00:07:18,480
I get it.

112
00:07:21,400 --> 00:07:22,860
You're playing me, right?

113
00:07:23,080 --> 00:07:25,600
How could we possibly play you?

114
00:07:25,600 --> 00:07:27,200
We wouldn't dare mess with you, Mr. Xiao.

115
00:07:27,200 --> 00:07:28,130
Right? Exactly.

116
00:07:28,440 --> 00:07:29,900
You can't keep this act up.

117
00:07:31,600 --> 00:07:32,440
Officer,

118
00:07:32,840 --> 00:07:34,040
I have proof.

119
00:07:34,680 --> 00:07:36,600
Last night when these three kidnapped me,

120
00:07:36,600 --> 00:07:39,080
I cut Yang Gang's right arm.

121
00:07:39,360 --> 00:07:40,890
Make him take off his shirt.

122
00:07:41,159 --> 00:07:41,880
Take it off.

123
00:07:41,880 --> 00:07:43,740
I'll take it off. I'll take it off.

124
00:07:43,920 --> 00:07:45,560
How rude.

125
00:07:46,720 --> 00:07:47,520
Do it.

126
00:07:48,000 --> 00:07:49,520
I'm doing it, Officer.

127
00:07:51,400 --> 00:07:52,640
Easy, easy.

128
00:07:52,640 --> 00:07:53,400
Ouch.

129
00:07:54,159 --> 00:07:55,520
I did pull a muscle recently.

130
00:07:55,520 --> 00:07:56,440
But look, Officer.

131
00:07:56,440 --> 00:07:58,120
There's definitely no cut.

132
00:07:58,120 --> 00:08:01,600
It's just a muscle strain.

133
00:08:01,840 --> 00:08:03,240
Ouch, take it easy. Ouch.

134
00:08:06,280 --> 00:08:08,080
Alright, put your shirt back on.

135
00:08:08,280 --> 00:08:09,800
See? Put it on.

136
00:08:12,680 --> 00:08:14,640
Officer, something's wrong.

137
00:08:14,640 --> 00:08:15,760
You have to investigate.

138
00:08:15,760 --> 00:08:16,760
I clearly saw last night,

139
00:08:16,760 --> 00:08:18,080
that it was the three of them who kidnapped me.

140
00:08:18,080 --> 00:08:19,760
What are you doing? Sit down.

141
00:08:20,120 --> 00:08:21,520
This is a police station.

142
00:08:22,080 --> 00:08:24,320
Regarding your report of being kidnapped,

143
00:08:24,320 --> 00:08:25,600
we will investigate thoroughly.

144
00:08:25,600 --> 00:08:27,680
But Yang Gang and his friends,

145
00:08:27,680 --> 00:08:28,940
seem to be in the clear.

146
00:08:29,120 --> 00:08:30,240
You three can go.
- Yes, sir.

147
00:08:30,240 --> 00:08:31,500
Officer, I have to say,

148
00:08:31,600 --> 00:08:32,760
thank you for your hard work.

149
00:08:32,760 --> 00:08:34,520
Sorry for all the trouble. Really.

150
00:08:34,520 --> 00:08:36,360
Yes. We'll repay you later.

151
00:08:36,440 --> 00:08:37,240
Thank you.

152
00:08:37,240 --> 00:08:38,039
Thank you, Officer.

153
00:08:38,039 --> 00:08:40,200
Mr. Xiao definitely got the wrong guys.

154
00:08:40,200 --> 00:08:41,440
He really made a mistake.

155
00:08:41,440 --> 00:08:43,100
His eyes played tricks on him.

156
00:08:43,240 --> 00:08:44,039
Fine.

157
00:08:45,360 --> 00:08:46,160
We'll

158
00:08:47,720 --> 00:08:49,000
see you later.

159
00:08:50,320 --> 00:08:53,080
Okay, we're leaving now.

160
00:08:53,400 --> 00:08:54,960
Thank you, Officer.

161
00:08:55,200 --> 00:08:55,800
Thank you.

162
00:08:58,400 --> 00:08:59,130
Don't worry.

163
00:08:59,280 --> 00:09:00,280
Trust the police.

164
00:09:00,400 --> 00:09:01,840
We'll get you justice.

165
00:09:13,520 --> 00:09:14,320
Yongzi.

166
00:09:15,400 --> 00:09:16,960
Xiaofang is really good at this.

167
00:09:16,960 --> 00:09:19,480
Of course. She's my wife, after all.

168
00:09:19,480 --> 00:09:21,320
Stop it. We're not married yet.

169
00:09:22,280 --> 00:09:24,040
This is a folk remedy from my hometown.

170
00:09:24,040 --> 00:09:26,480
You can use pigskin for cuts and scrapes like this.

171
00:09:26,480 --> 00:09:27,160
It heals fast,

172
00:09:27,160 --> 00:09:28,220
and stops the pain.

173
00:09:30,840 --> 00:09:31,640
Gang,

174
00:09:32,560 --> 00:09:35,160
this watch is really something.

175
00:09:35,440 --> 00:09:36,720
It's high-end.

176
00:09:37,480 --> 00:09:38,740
You're so smart, Gang.

177
00:09:39,040 --> 00:09:40,240
You came up with this plan

178
00:09:40,240 --> 00:09:43,040
to make Xiao Tianman dig his own grave.

179
00:09:46,840 --> 00:09:48,500
This must be worth thousands.

180
00:09:51,800 --> 00:09:53,480
I've seen this on TV.

181
00:09:53,800 --> 00:09:56,440
It has an alarm and you can dive with it.

182
00:09:57,440 --> 00:09:59,170
It's very popular in Hong Kong.

183
00:10:00,440 --> 00:10:03,640
Look, it's almost 8 o'clock.

184
00:10:04,360 --> 00:10:05,240
Xiao Tianman

185
00:10:05,560 --> 00:10:07,880
sets an alarm for 11 every day

186
00:10:07,880 --> 00:10:09,080
to take his medicine.

187
00:10:09,200 --> 00:10:12,640
We'll set the clock forward by 3 hours.

188
00:10:13,920 --> 00:10:15,250
When the alarm goes off,

189
00:10:15,360 --> 00:10:18,280
he'll think we kidnapped him at 11.

190
00:10:20,200 --> 00:10:22,800
We'll go pick a fight with Chen right now

191
00:10:22,800 --> 00:10:24,060
and come back before 2.

192
00:10:25,880 --> 00:10:28,000
We'll say the watch showed 11,

193
00:10:28,640 --> 00:10:29,900
when it was actually 2.

194
00:10:30,760 --> 00:10:31,600
That way,

195
00:10:31,600 --> 00:10:35,280
Chen will be our alibi witness.

196
00:10:39,000 --> 00:10:40,560
Luo Zhengqiang! Get out here!

197
00:10:40,560 --> 00:10:41,360
Who is it?

198
00:10:45,560 --> 00:10:46,360
Who is it?

199
00:10:47,360 --> 00:10:48,290
Luo Zhengqiang!

200
00:10:52,240 --> 00:10:53,640
Where is Luo Zhengqiang?

201
00:10:53,640 --> 00:10:55,700
Stop hiding and get the hell out here!

202
00:10:57,400 --> 00:10:58,280
Mr. Sun,

203
00:10:58,680 --> 00:10:59,560
this is my home.

204
00:11:00,000 --> 00:11:00,960
Don't be so aggressive.

205
00:11:00,960 --> 00:11:02,320
Let's sit down and talk.
